{"tid":1743383,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"再講多次 咩叫\"靜靜地贏\" & \"我無嘢講\"","createTime":"2019-11-21T07:26:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-21T17:14:03.000Z","uid":57073,"like":87,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"654f603fc5a315e0102c16e1ada1c7752d56e051","tid":1743383,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:26:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yuihiT8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyuihiT8.jpg&h=bdd461a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我唔明好多人到底係想出來威然後坐10年暴動 定 無人知你做過D乜做一個無名英雄<br />\n<br />\n你地唔好諗住Facebook好安全<br />\n你唔會知有d 咩人會出賣你 / 監視住你<br />\n<br />\n成日都要Post D 相 D 片出來<br />\n唔直接講去過都暗示被人知咁<br />\n又影下地下d磚 又影下d火<br />\n呢d 相就係最好嘅證據證明你去過現場<br />\n影過d 磚影過d 火就啫係你同d 暴徒好近啦<br />\n你又share過D 文宣啫係你知有人集結啦<br />\n咁就10年<br />\n<br />\n唔該啦 忍下手<br />\n你唔係要做KOL 你係要贏<br />\n<br />\n李安然大律師 - 我無嘢講<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=RvyMaYBa1hE&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRvyMaYBa1hE%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=1ClhXrEf11pGEOLLd6ameBPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=174c7c89\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=RvyMaYBa1hE&amp;feature=youtu.be</a>"},{"pid":"910248a3d3bf4937c64e6f2312d9f78f31758719","tid":1743383,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:27:06.000Z","msg":"星期五夜晚，各區商場和理非唱歌，區選前最大型和理非行動，想問下你會唔會參與？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1743281\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1743281</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"76c7da0b696a42b2664d23b59181bd4013277388","tid":1743383,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:33:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de79cfe8d4cc8d1d1cfe771cc6097b3c851e7a2c","tid":1743383,"uid":57073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-21T07:35:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.